    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>nfsマウントについて</h2>

<p>サーバ側</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ sudo aptitude -y install nfs-kernel-server</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>sudo emacs /etc/exportsを編集</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>/mnt 192.168.1.0/24(rw,sync,fsid=0,no_root_squash,no_subtree_check)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>クライアント側</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ sudo aptitude install nfs-common
</span><span class='line'>sudo emacs /etc/fstab</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>fstabを編集</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>192.168.1.1:/mnt       /mnt/nfs_server      nfs     rsize=8192,wsize=8192,hard,intr    0       0</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
<a href="http://itmst.blog71.fc2.com/blog-entry-89.html">ここ</a>にexportsやfstabのオプションについての記述あり。</p>
